 ạlqrạr- sạmḥnạ yạ fạdynạ bạrknạ yạ yswʿ
 ʿywnnạ bttrjạk mlyạnẗ bạldmwʿ
 1- ạ̹nt ạ̹lhnạ ạlḥy ạ̹nt ạlly qryb jạy
 htyjy wtʿzynạ wtmsḥ ạldmwʿ
 2- dạymaⁿạ ntʿdy̱ ʿlyk wạlʿạlm bygẖrynạ
 qwynạ yạ yswʿ mn fḍlk yạ yswʿ
 3- wlạ ḥạjẗ nstạhlhạ mn ạlly ạnt btdyhạlnạ
 dy mḥbtk gẖmrtnạ nsjd lk fy kẖsẖwʿ
 4- ʿly̱ ạlqlwb btqrʿ wṭwby̱ lly ysmʿ
 wytwb twbẗ mn qlbh twbẗ mn gẖyr rjwʿ</lyrics>
